column1:
select cve_periodo,case when cve_institucion='068011' and cve_periodo>=201312 then '068014' else cve_institucion end as cve_institucion,
case when rango_limite_credito is null then 999
else rango_limite_credito
end as rango_limite_credito
,sum(tarjetas) numero_tarjetas
from db_TdC..DM_tc_banxico
group by cve_periodo,cve_institucion,case when rango_limite_credito is null then 999 else rango_limite_credito end
